"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-01-andy-murray-heartbroken-miss-fairytale-ending-paris-olympics-21345915\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Andy Murraywas left heartbroken to miss out on a 'fairytale ending' at theParisOlympics as he officially entered retirement on Thursday night.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 142, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic tennis tournament wasMurray's 'last ever' eventin the sport, with the British icon eliminated alongsideDan Evansin the men's doubles last eight.\", \"from\": 144, \"to\": 300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 226, \"end\": 233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9977206077151071, \"rank\": 0.0022665789646059632, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray and Evansconjured up two rollercoaster winsand were just one victory away from earning themselves a spot in a medal match.\", \"from\": 302, \"to\": 431, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 302, \"end\": 308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6753802971264717e-19, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Team GB duo were unable to battle past Team USA's Taylor Fritz and Tommy Paul, though, who beat the Brits 6-2 6-4 inMurray's final professional outing.\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 476, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.7727168179823836, \"rank\": 0.27718689001977925, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": 