s it.'\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 931, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9981848624297195, \"rank\": 0.0015112440368939444, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Quizzed about his plans for retirement, the 37-year-old former world No.1 added: 'I have four children below the age of eight\\u2026 So lay-ins do not happen!\", \"from\": 961, \"to\": 1113, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"they are up at 5am or 6am.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not sure what I will do tonight.\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I will probably go back to the Village and find some pins for my collection!\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then, I dunno.\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1276, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I can do whatever I want now.\", \"from\": 1277, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I want to go home and spend time with my family.'\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked about how it feels to finish his career, two-time Wimbledon champion and double Olympic gold medallist Murray said: 'I feel good.\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1471, \"end\": 1477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6753802971264717e-19, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Never even liked tennis anyway.\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I have been ready for this moment for the last few months since I had the operation on my back - I knew it was the right time and I feel lucky to come and compete here.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am grateful to Dan Evans for putting in the effort he did to giving us a good chance to having a great run.\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1721, \"end\": 1730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"score\": 0.9827598100865458, \"rank\": 0.01754262734119406, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am looking forward to stopping now.\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1851, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'I mean it was a great run (in Paris) and we lost to two top players today.\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1884, \"end\": 1889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999605265665, \"rank\": 3.947332241080815e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are both top tennis players, we would have had to play very well to win that match and we did not.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 2032, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We got into it at the end, but if we found that form earlier we could have caused them problems, but it wasn't to be.\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2152, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We did make the quarters, but if you get through that match you get an opportunity to win a medal.'\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2254, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Hollywood megastar set to perform death-defying stunt during Olympics closing ceremony  ArrowMORE:Clare Balding on verge of breaking down while commentating at Olympics  ArrowMORE:Andy Murray tennis retirement confirmed af